Island Fighting (Time-Life World War II Series)
Time-Life Books | 1978 | ISBN: 0809424886 | English | 216 pages | PDF | 34.6 MB

This book is typical of the Time-Life Series. Included are hundreds of great photographs, detailed maps, and line drawings that aid the narratives in giving a great overview of the war in the pacific as the allies moved toward Japan
